  "body": "## Implementation\r\n\r\n- [x] Add params, config and types https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/4568\r\n- [x] Make `c-kzg` library available for Lodestar. Add native bindings for `ethereum/c-kzg-eip4844` https://github.com/dankrad/c-kzg/pull/3\r\n- [x] Block proposing\r\n  - Add new engine API `engine_getBlobsV1`\r\n  - Cache returned blobs in beacon to not modify validator cycle code\r\n  - Publish to gossip topic, depending on fork\r\n- [x] Block processing / import\r\n  - Update chain `processBlock` to take block + (maybe) blobs pair\r\n  - Validate blobs `is_data_available`, running KZG crypto\r\n  - Store blobs to database + migrate from hot to cold on finalization + prune old blobs < MIN_EPOCHS_FOR_BLOBS_SIDECARS_REQUESTS\r\n- [x] Add p2p ResResp methods `BeaconBlockAndBlobsSidecarByRoot` + `BlobsSidecarsByRange`\r\n  - Update register / unregister logic to active those topics only post-eip4844\r\n- [x] Add p2p gossip topic `beacon_block_and_blobs_sidecar`\r\n\r\nFinal PR\r\n\r\n- https://github.com/ChainSafe/lodestar/pull/4774\r\n\r\n## Devnet items\r\n\r\nCC: @g11tech \r\n\r\n## Pending spec PRs\r\n\r\n- [x] https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/3185\r\n- [x] https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/3174\r\n- [x] https://github.com/ethereum/consensus-specs/pull/3181\r\n- [x] https://github.com/ethereum/beacon-APIs/pull/286\r\n",
